ent-AU14VAIPOclothingequipmentvendor = VAIPO apparel vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Vanguard Arrow Incorporated mercenary apparel used by their Primary Operations branch. Standard issue aboard naval vessels, military outposts, corporate-science installations and civilian colonies across the frontier. Manufactured to outfit personnel rapidly following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For full operational readiness, select one item from each section: fatigues with a webbing, footwear, gloves, headgear, armor, backpack, belt and a pouch.
ent-AU14VAIPOequipmentvendor = VAIPO equipment vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of standard Vanguard Arrow Incorporated mercenary equipment used by their Primary Operations branch. Stocked with medical supplies and field gear for rapid deployment following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization. The interface is intentionally simple, even someone with tunnel-vision and frostbite can operate it.
        Rapid-issue protocol: prioritize medical supplies, a ration pack, an e-tool and sandbags.
ent-AU14VAIPOcorpsmanvendor = VAIPO medical vendor
    .desc =
        An automated medical rack, hooked up to a compact stock of trauma supplies for Vanguard Arrow Incorporated mercenary medics used by their Primary Operations branch. Standard issue for corpsmen aboard naval vessels, outposts and colonies where casualties arrive faster than reinforcements. Designed for rapid reconstitution of combat medics following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency call-up.
        Corpsman protocol: select the essential equipment set, storage and limited medications.
ent-AU14VAIPOaircrewvendor = VAIPO aircrew vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Vanguard Arrow Incorporated mercenary aircrew flight and support gear used by their Primary Operations branch. Engineered to get flight personnel flight-ready in seconds after cryogenic hypersleep or scramble orders.
        Aircrew protocol: select a set of fatigues, the essential medical equipment and storage kit.
ent-AU14VAIPOcommandequipmentvendor = VAIPO command vendor
    .desc = An automated command rack, hooked up to a restricted storage of Vanguard Arrow Incorporated mercenary leadership equipment used by their Primary Operations branch. Manufactured to equip commanding personnel following cryogenic hypersleep or an emergency directive is issued.
ent-AU14VAIPOSGequipmentvendor = VAIPO automatic rifleman equipment vendor
    .desc = An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Vanguard Arrow Incorporated mercenary light-machine gun systems used by their Primary Operations branch. Standard issue for designated automatic riflemen on naval vessels and high-threat outposts. Built to bring fire support online rapidly after cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
ent-AU14VAIPOsectionleaderequipmentvendor = VAIPO section leader vendor
    .desc = An automated equipment rack, hooked up to a compact storage of Vanguard Arrow Incorporated mercenary section-leadership equipment used by their Primary Operations branch. Designed for immediate readiness following cryogenic hypersleep or rapid mobilization orders.
ent-AU14VAIPOWeaponsVendor = VAIPO weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Vanguard Arrow Incorporated mercenary weaponry used by their Primary Operations branch. Standard issue across the frontier where threats can appear without warning. Engineered to arm personnel in seconds following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For immediate combat readiness: select a primary weapon kit and a sidearm.
ent-AU14VAIPOSpecialWeaponsVendor = VAIPO special weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated special weapons rack, hooked up to a restricted armory of Vanguard Arrow Incorporated heavy and breaching mercenary ordnance used by their Primary Operations branch. Standard issue only for qualified operators. Engineered to deliver overwhelming firepower the instant cryogenic hypersleep ends or an emergency mobilization is called.
        Special weapons protocol: one weapon system of choice with a full ammunition loadout and explosives.
ent-AU14VAIPORequisitionVendor = VAIPO automated requisitions vendor
    .desc = An automated supply rack hooked up to a big storage of various firearms, ammunitions, explosives, load carrying equipment and other miscellaneous items.
